data.description: Welcome to this 3-level townhome! This interior unit offers 4 Bedrooms and 2 full Bathrooms. You'll find hardwood floors on the main level and hallway upstairs. The main level has a spacious Living Room, a formal Dining Room, and Kitchen. The bright kitchen features stainless steel appliances and white cabinets. Upstairs has 4 Bedrooms, including the Primary, and 2 full bathrooms. If you need an in-home office, the attic on the 3rd floor might be just what you're looking for! An unfinished basement with a dryer is ready for your creative touch! Great home! Call now to schedule your showing!
